-><b><i><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;\">1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></i></b><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">Traduire en&nbsp;<b>formation permanente</b>&nbsp;les nombreux enseignements du songe&nbsp;:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">Â«&nbsp;Faites attention&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;cherchez Ã  comprendre&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;prÃ©voyez et prÃªchez&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;ce que vous prÃªchez, faites-le vous-mÃªmes&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;aimez la tradition et transmettez-la&nbsp;Â»â€¦<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><i><span style=\"font-size: 4pt; line-height: 5.706666946411133px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><i>2.</i></b>&nbsp;Le jeune nous rappelle aussi que nous devons avoir le souci des&nbsp;<b>vocations&nbsp;</b>et de la&nbsp;<b>formation des nouvelles gÃ©nÃ©rations&nbsp;</b>:&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Soyez avisÃ©s pour accepter les novices&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;soyez forts pour les former&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;soyez prudents pour les admettre&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;Ã©prouvez-les&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;; Â«&nbsp;renvoyez ceux qui sont lÃ©gers et changeants&nbsp;Â»â€¦<o:p></o:p></i></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 4pt; line-height: 5.706666946411133px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 21.3pt;\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">3.</span></i></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Enfin il nous rappelle&nbsp;<b>la fidÃ©litÃ© au Fondateur</b>, moyennant la connaissance et la mise en pratique des&nbsp;<b>Constitutions</b>.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">EN GUISE DE CONCLUSION<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 4pt; line-height: 5.706666946411133px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 14.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; font-family: &quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">CommunautÃ©s et individus, Ã©couterons-nous ces avertissements&nbsp;? Cela met en jeu&nbsp;<b>lâ€™avenir de la CongrÃ©gation</b>.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" sty