>, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn26\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref26\" name=\"_ftn26\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[26]</span></span></span></a><i>&nbsp;Â«&nbsp;Salomon se plaÃ§a devant lâ€™autel du Seigneur, en face de toute lâ€™assemblÃ©e dâ€™IsraÃ«l ; il Ã©tendit les mains vers le ciel et fit cette priÃ¨re : \" Seigneur, Dieu dâ€™IsraÃ«l, il nâ€™y a pas de Dieu comme toi, ni lÃ -haut dans les cieux, ni sur la terre ici-bas ; car tu gardes ton Alliance et ta fidÃ©litÃ© envers tes serviteurs, quand ils marchent devant toi de tout leur cÅ“ur.\"&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(1R 8,22-23).<o:p></o:p></p></div><div id=\"ftn27\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref27\" name=\"_ftn27\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[27]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Le Christ&nbsp;<i>Â«PantocratorÂ»</i>&nbsp;est une reprÃ©sentation privilÃ©giÃ©e de lâ€™art byzantin&nbsp;; le Christ est reprÃ©sentÃ© gÃ©nÃ©ralement assis sur un trÃ´ne de gloire, tenant le Livre des Saintes Ã‰critures dans la main gauche et de la main droite esquissant un geste de bÃ©nÃ©diction.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn28\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref28\" name=\"_ftn28\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[28]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Ainsi, la Loi est sainte&nbsp;; le commandement est saint, juste et bon.&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(Rm 7,12).<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn29\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref29\" name=\"_ftn29\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[29]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;â€¦ amour quâ€™il montre envers nos pÃ¨res, mÃ©moire de son alliance sainte&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(Lc 1,72).<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn30\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref30\" name=\"_ftn30\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[30]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">Â«&nbsp;â€¦ quand&nbsp;</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">[le Fils de lâ€™homme]&nbsp;<i>viendra dans la gloire de son PÃ¨re avec les saints anges.&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(Mc&nbsp;8,38).</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn31\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref31\" name=\"_ft