, LAS-Rome, 2016, p. 85.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn39\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref39\" name=\"_ftn39\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[39]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Ibidem, pp. 83-84.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn40\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref40\" name=\"_ftn40\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">[40]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">&nbsp;Par exemple&nbsp;:&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Venez, mes fils, Ã©coutez-moi, que je vous enseigne la crainte du Seigneur.&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(Ps 33,12). Ou&nbsp;:&nbsp;<i>Â« Servez le Seigneur dans l\'allÃ©gresse&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(Ps 99,2).&nbsp;Ibidem pp. 116-117.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn41\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref41\" name=\"_ftn41\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[41]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Un entretien ultÃ©rieur traitera de la saintetÃ© des jeunes.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn42\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref42\" name=\"_ftn42\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[42]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;MB<i>&nbsp;</i>III, 490 citÃ© par Morand WIRTH, op. cit. p. 167.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn43\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref43\" name=\"_ftn43\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[43]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">PAPE FRANÃ‡OIS,&nbsp;<i>Gaudete et Exsultate, Exhortation Apostolique sur lâ€™appel Ã  la SaintetÃ© dans le monde actuel</i>, Rome, 19 mars 2018.</span></span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn44\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref44\" name=\"_ftn44\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[44]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Câ€™est la traduction de la&nbsp;<i>Bible de JÃ©rusalem</i>. La&nbsp;<i>Bible de la Liturgie</i>&nbsp;traduit au futur&nbsp;:<i>&nbsp;Â«Vous vous sanctifierez et vous serez saints car moi, je suis saint&nbsp;Â»</i>. Ce futur nâ€™est pas hypothÃ©tique car la suite du verset â€“ Ã  lâ€™indicatif prÃ©sent â€“ laisse entendre un fait dÃ©jÃ  accompli puisque la saintetÃ© contagieuse de Dieu est immÃ©diatement opÃ©rante. Cela ne veut pas dire que lâ€™homme doit rester inactif mais il doit emprunter dÃ©libÃ©rÃ©ment la voie de la saintetÃ© avec la certitude que Dieu lâ€™y prÃ©cÃ©deraâ€¦&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn45\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref45\" name=\"_ftn45\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"IT\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[45]</span></span></span></span></a><span lang=\"IT\">&nbsp;</span><i>Â« Ne savez-vous pas que vous Ãªtes un sanctuaire de Dieu, et que lâ€™Esprit de Dieu habite en vous&nbsp;?&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;<b>(1Co 3,16)</b>. -&nbsp;<i>Â« Et voici la preuve que vous Ãªtes des fils&nbsp;: Dieu a envoyÃ© lâ€™Esprit de son Fils dans nos cÅ“urs, et cet Esprit crie \"Abba&nbsp;!\", câ€™est-Ã -dire&nbsp;: PÃ¨re&nbsp;!&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;<b>(Ga 4,6)</b>. -&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;â€¦ vous avez reÃ§u un Esprit qui fait de vous des fils&nbsp;; et câ€™est en lui que nous crions Â«&nbsp;Abba&nbsp;!&nbsp;Â», câ€™est-Ã -dire&nbsp;: PÃ¨re&nbsp;! Câ€™est donc lâ€™Esprit Saint lui-mÃªme qui atteste Ã  notre esprit que nous sommes enfants de Dieu.&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;<b>(Rm 8,15-16)</b>.<o:p></o:p></p></div><div id=\"ftn46\"><p class=\"M