de l\'Ã‰glise</i>&nbsp;dans la foi, eut d\'emblÃ©e la perspective de&nbsp;<i>l\'unitÃ© des chrÃ©tiens</i>. Sans doute est-ce la raison de cette quadruple qualification de lâ€™Ã‰glise&nbsp;: une, sainte, catholique (universelle), apostolique.</span></span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn49\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref49\" name=\"_ftn49\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[49]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\">Â«&nbsp;Or, il y avait dans leur synagogue un homme tourmentÃ© par un esprit impur, qui se mit Ã  crier&nbsp;: \"Que nous veux-tu, JÃ©sus de Nazareth&nbsp;? Es-tu venu pour nous perdre&nbsp;? Je sais qui tu es&nbsp;: tu es le Saint de Dieu.\"&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;</span></i><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\">(</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\">Mc 1, 23-24).</span></span><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.6pt;\"></span><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn50\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 15.693333625793457px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref50\" name=\"_ftn50\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[50]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Cette nouvelle traduction de la&nbsp;<i>Bible de la Liturgie</i>&nbsp;ne rend pas assez compte du fait que&nbsp;<u>ce peuple est&nbsp;<i>un peuple acquis par Dieu</i></u>, ainsi que le traduit la&nbsp;<i>Bible de JÃ©rusalem</i>&nbsp;:&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;</i></span><i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Mais vous, vous Ãªtes une race Ã©lue, un sacerdoce royal, une nation sainte,&nbsp;<u>un peuple acquis</u>&nbsp;</span></i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">[par Dieu]<i>, pour proclamer les louanges de Celui qui vous a appelÃ©s des tÃ©nÃ¨bres Ã  son admirable lumiÃ¨re&nbsp;Â»</i>.</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn51\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref51\" name=\"_ftn51\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[51]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Lâ€™Ã‰glise prend Ã  juste titre lâ€™aspect de la pÃ©cheresse, parce que le Christ aussi a pris l\'apparence du pÃ©cheur&nbsp;Â»</i>(SAINT AMBROISE,&nbsp;<i>Commentaire de lâ€™Ã‰vangile de Luc</i>&nbsp;VI, 21).<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn52\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref52\" name=\"_ftn52\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; lin