&nbsp;Ce point sera traitÃ© dans un entretien ultÃ©rieur.</span><o:p></o:p></p></div><div id=\"ftn58\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref58\" name=\"_ftn58\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[58]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Câ€™est une erreur, et mÃªme une hÃ©rÃ©sie, de vouloir bannir la vie dÃ©vote de la compagnie des soldats, de la boutique des artisans, de la cour des princes, du mÃ©nage des gens mariÃ©s. (â€¦) OÃ¹ que nous soyons, nous pouvons et devons aspirer Ã  la vie parfaite.&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(<i>Introduction Ã  la vie dÃ©vote</i>, I, 3).</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn59\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref59\" name=\"_ftn59\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[59]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;In&nbsp;<i>TraitÃ© de lâ€™amour de Dieu</i>, VIII, 11.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn60\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref60\" name=\"_ftn60\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12p