yle=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[66]</span></span></span></span></a><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Ibidem p. 114.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn67\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref67\" name=\"_ftn67\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[67]</span></span></span></span></a><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Giovanni BOSCO,&nbsp;<i>Regole o Costituzioni della SocietÃ  di S. Francesco di Sales</i>, Turin 1885,&nbsp;<i>Introduzione</i>.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Cf.&nbsp;<i>Constitutions de la SociÃ©tÃ© de saint FranÃ§ois de Sales,&nbsp;</i>Ã‰dition de mai 2015, p. 218.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn68\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref68\" name=\"_ftn68\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[68]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Le thÃ¨me de la saintetÃ© proposÃ©e aux jeunes par Don Bosco sera traitÃ© dans un entretien ultÃ©rieur.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn69\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref69\" name=\"_ftn69\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[69]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Je me limiterai volontairement aux&nbsp;<b>sacrements de lâ€™initiation chrÃ©tienne</b>&nbsp;(BaptÃªme, Confirmation, Eucharistie, et jâ€™y ajoute RÃ©conciliation) car ce sont ces sacrements surtout que nous avons Ã  cÃ©lÃ©brer dans notre pastorale des jeunes principalement en Ã©cole. Mon propos nâ€™est pas de faire une thÃ©ologie exhaustive de ces sacrements mais dâ€™Ã©voquer leur cÃ©lÃ©bration comme expression de notre foi, vÃ©hicule de la GrÃ¢ce et donc moyen de sanctification.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn70\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref70\" name=\"_ftn70\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[70]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Cf. CEC 1265, 1275.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn71\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref71\" name=\"_ftn71\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[71]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">Depuis les dÃ©buts de la&nbsp;<b>CrÃ©ation</b>&nbsp;(<i>Gn</i>&nbsp;1,2), en passant par le&nbsp;<b>DÃ©luge</b><i>&nbsp;</i>(<i>Gn</i>&nbsp;7,17) jusquâ€™Ã  lâ€™<b>Exode</b>&nbsp;(<i>Ex</i>&nbsp;14,21-22), sans oublier lâ€™entrÃ©e en&nbsp;<b>Terre Promise</b>&nbsp;Ã  travers les eaux du Jourdain (<i>Jos</i>&nbsp;3,17).&nbsp;<b>Ã‰zÃ©kiel</b>&nbsp;exploitera ce thÃ¨me de lâ€™eau en se faisant lâ€™interprÃ¨te de lâ€™espÃ©rance dâ€™IsraÃ«l pour une nouvelle alliance (36,25-26).</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn72\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref72\" name=\"_ftn72\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[72]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Cf. CEC 1265 et 1279.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn73\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref73\" name=\"_ftn73\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[73]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Cf.&nbsp;<i>Lumen Gentium</i>&nbsp;30-36.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn74\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText