oteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[102]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;CONGRÃ‰GATION POUR LES RELIGIEUX ET LES INSTITUTS SÃ‰CULIERS,&nbsp;<i>Mutuae Relationes</i>&nbsp;[Les rapports Mutuels], Directives de base sur les rapports entre les Ã©vÃªques et les religieux dans lâ€™Ã‰glise, Rome, 14 mai 1978, n.11.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn103\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref103\" name=\"_ftn103\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[103]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;CONCILE VATICAN II,&nbsp;<i>LUMEN GENTIUM</i>&nbsp;[Le Christ est la lumiÃ¨re des peuples],&nbsp;<i>Constitution Dogmatique sur lâ€™Ã‰glise,</i>&nbsp;Rome, 21 novembre 1964.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn104\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref104\" name=\"_ftn104\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[104]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Celui-ci parle du don charismatique&nbsp;: quel quâ€™il soit (don de sagesse, de science, de foi, de guÃ©rison), il sâ€™agit toujours dâ€™un don 