p;Â»</i>&nbsp;(P. CARAVA, Centenaire de la mort de Don Bosco, Lyon, janvier 1988).<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn172\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref172\" name=\"_ftn172\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[172]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;ACG 300, p. 20 dans lâ€™Ã©dition franÃ§aise.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn173\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref173\" name=\"_ftn173\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[173]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i>Actes du Chapitre SupÃ©rieur</i>&nbsp;56, p. 934.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn174\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref174\" name=\"_ftn174\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[174]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;MB XVII, 890. Voir aussi MB X, 1059&nbsp;; MB XII, 459.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn175\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: 