id=\"ftn177\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref177\" name=\"_ftn177\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[177]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i>Actes du Chapitre SupÃ©rieur</i>&nbsp;55, p. 924<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn178\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref178\" name=\"_ftn178\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[178]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Cf. ACG 300, p. 28 dans lâ€™Ã©dition franÃ§aise</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Le PÃ¨re parle en 1981, aprÃ¨s la crise grave des annÃ©es 1960-1970, en Occident particuliÃ¨rement.<i></i></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn179\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref179\" name=\"_ftn179\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[179]</span></span></span></span></a><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Cf. Eugenio CERIA,&nbsp;<i>Annali della SocietÃ  Salesiana</i>&nbsp;I, pp.747-748.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Il sâ€™agit dâ€™un ordre religieux fondÃ© Ã  Rome au 17<sup>Ã¨me</sup>&nbsp;siÃ¨cle par St Joseph Calasanz (1557-1648) et dÃ©diÃ© Ã  lâ€™Ã©vangÃ©lisation par lâ€™Ã©ducation des enfants, surtout les plus pauvres, pour lesquels il professe un quatriÃ¨me vÅ“u spÃ©cial.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn180\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref180\" name=\"_ftn180\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[180]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;SYNODE DES Ã‰VÃŠQUES, XVÃ¨me AssemblÃ©e GÃ©nÃ©rale Ordinaire,&nbsp;<i>Les Jeunes, la foi et le discernement vocationnel, Document final</i>, Rome, 27 octobre 2018, n.101.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn181\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref181\" name=\"_ftn181\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[181]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Le CG21 sâ€™est tenu Ã  Rome du 31 octobre 1977 au 12 fÃ©vrier 1978, sur le thÃ¨me&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Les SalÃ©siens, Ã©vangÃ©lisateurs des jeunes&n