pan style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">Â«&nbsp;Fais de ta vie un \"Je tâ€™aime\"&nbsp;!&nbsp;Â»</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">, tel Ã©tait le thÃ¨me de la visite du Pape Jean Paul II Ã  Lyon, en octobre 1986.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn208\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref208\" name=\"_ftn208\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[208]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;MB V, 716.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn209\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref209\" name=\"_ftn209\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[209]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;MB VIII, 428&nbsp;: Lettre du 9 juin 1867, Dimanche de PentecÃ´te,&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Ã€ Don Rua et Ã  mes autres chers fils de saint FranÃ§ois rÃ©sidant Ã  Turin&nbsp;Â»</i>. Nos Constitutions insistent sur ce Â«&nbsp;chemin de notre sanctification&nbsp;Â» qui est dâ€™Â«&nbsp;Ãªtre signes et porteurs de lâ€™amour de Dieu pour les jeunes&nbsp;Â» (C 2).<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn210\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref210\" name=\"_ftn210\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFoot