en Gn 17,5 et 15,5&nbsp;: Â«&nbsp;<i>EspÃ©rant contre toute espÃ©rance, il a cru&nbsp;; ainsi est-il devenu le pÃ¨re dâ€™un grand nombre de nations, selon cette parole : Telle sera la descendance que tu auras&nbsp;!</i>Â» (Rm 4,18).</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn221\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref221\" name=\"_ftn221\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[221]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Aujourdâ€™hui, la liste officielle sâ€™Ã©lÃ¨ve Ã  168 membres&nbsp;: cf. ACG 429, pp. 42-43 dans lâ€™Ã©dition en langue franÃ§aise&nbsp;: au 31 dÃ©cembre 2018,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">notre Postulation recensait 168 saints, bienheureux, vÃ©nÃ©rables,&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">serviteurs de Dieu, clercs, consacrÃ©s ou laÃ¯cs, ainsi rÃ©partis&nbsp;:</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\">&nbsp;9&nbsp;<u>canonisÃ©s</u>&nbsp;(dont 1 jeune et 2 martyrs)&nbsp;; 118&nbsp;<u>bÃ©atifiÃ©s</u>&nbsp;(dont 2 jeunes, et 105 martyrs dont 5 jeunes)&nbsp;; 17&nbsp;<u>vÃ©nÃ©rables</u>&nbsp;et 24&nbsp;<u>serviteurs de Dieu</u>&nbsp;(dont 11 martyrs).</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: red;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn222\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref222\" name=\"_ftn222\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-fam