.1200008392334px;\">[255]</span></span></span></span></a><i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.5pt;\">Â«&nbsp;JÃ©sus, voyant sa mÃ¨re, et prÃ¨s dâ€™elle le disciple quâ€™il aimait, dit Ã  sa mÃ¨re&nbsp;: \"&nbsp;Femme, voici ton fils.\"&nbsp;Â»</span></span></i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: -0.5pt;\">&nbsp;(Jn 19,26).</span><i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"></span></i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn256\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref256\" name=\"_ftn256\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: -0.4pt;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px; letter-spacing: -0.4pt;\">[256]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: -0.4pt;\">&nbsp;Cf. JEAN PAUL II, Encyclique&nbsp;<i>Redemptoris Mater</i>&nbsp;[la MÃ¨re du RÃ©dempteur], Rome, 25 mars 1987, nÂ° 39.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn257\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref257\" name=\"_ftn257\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[257]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Les protestants croient en Marie MÃ¨re de Dieu comme lâ€™exprime le Concile dâ€™Ã‰phÃ¨se. Cependant ils prÃ©fÃ¨rent appeler Marie Â«&nbsp;MÃ¨re du Christ&nbsp;Â», terme qui leur paraÃ®t moins ambigu.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn258\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref258\" name=\"_ftn258\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"IT\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[258]</span></span></span></span></a><span lang=\"IT\">&nbsp;</span><i>Â«&nbsp;Nâ€™est-il pas le fils du charpentier&nbsp;? Sa mÃ¨re ne sâ€™appelle-t-elle pas Marie, et ses frÃ¨res&nbsp;: Jacques, Joseph, Simon et Jude&nbsp;? Et ses sÅ“urs ne sont-elles pas toutes chez nous&nbsp;? Alors, dâ€™oÃ¹ lui vient tout cela&nbsp;?&nbsp;Â»&nbsp;</i>(Mt 13,55-56).&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Quelquâ€™un lui dit&nbsp;: Â«&nbsp;Ta mÃ¨re et tes frÃ¨res sont lÃ , dehors, qui cherchent Ã  te parler.&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;(Mt 12,47).<o:p></o:p></p></div><div id=\"ftn259\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref259\" name=\"_ftn259\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[259]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<i>Lumen Gentium</i>&nbsp;60.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn260\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref260\" name=\"_ftn260\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[260]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Ibidem, chapitre VIII.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><span style=\"font-size: 3pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p></div><div id=\"ftn261\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref261\" name=\"_ftn261\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[261]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;MalgrÃ© la timiditÃ© de&nbsp;<i>Lumen Gentium</i>&nbsp;Ã  dÃ©clarer clairement Marie Â«&nbsp;MÃ¨re de lâ€™Ã‰glise&nbsp;Â», Paul VI lâ€™a fait :&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;Ã€ la gloire de la Bienheureuse Vierge, et pour notre consolation, nous dÃ©clarons la TrÃ¨s Sainte Vierge Marie MÃ¨re de lâ€™Ã‰glise, câ€™est-Ã -dire de tout le peuple chrÃ©tien â€“ tant des fidÃ¨les que des Pasteurs â€“ qui lâ€™invoque comme MÃ¨re aimable&nbsp;; et nous Ã©tablissons que le peuple chrÃ©tien tout entier honore dÃ©sormais avec plus de ferveur sous ce titre la MÃ¨re de Dieu, et lui adresse ses&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">suppliques.&nbsp;Â»</span></i><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\">&nbsp;(Discours de clÃ´ture de la III<sup>Ã¨me</sup>&nbsp;session du Concile Vatican II, 21 novembre 1964, nÂ° 30).</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn262\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref262\" name=\"_ftn262\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[262]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">Lâ€™Ã‰glise Catholique sâ€™est prononcÃ©e sur lâ€™un et sur lâ€™autre en en faisant des dogmes&nbsp;: en 1854 pour lâ€™ImmaculÃ©e Conception et en 1950 pour lâ€™Assomption de Marie.</span></span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn263\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref263\" name=\"_ftn263\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[263]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Ce quâ€™on appelle&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;pÃ©chÃ© originel&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;ne serait-ce pas arriver au moment de sa naissance dans un monde qui est dÃ©jÃ  le lieu du mal, des conflits, du pÃ©chÃ©&nbsp;? Ce conditionnement est imposÃ© Ã  tout homme qui vient au monde, et ne dÃ©pend en rien de la volontÃ© de chacun, mais favorise la tendance au mal sur la tendance au bien dans le jeu de la libertÃ©.</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn264\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref264\" name=\"_ftn264\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[264]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;PSEUDO JEAN,&nbsp;<i>Dormition de Marie</i>, nn. 6-26. Â«Le</span><span class=\"justification\"><i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;Seigneur appela sa mÃ¨re et lui dit : \"Marie&nbsp;!\". Elle rÃ©pondit :\"Me voici, Seigneur !\". Et le Seigneur lui dit : \"Ne t\'afflige pas, mais que ton cÅ“ur se rÃ©jouisse et soit dans l\'allÃ©gresse, car tu as obtenu la faveur de contempler la gloire qui me fut donnÃ©e par mon PÃ¨re\" (â€¦) Voici que maintenant ton prÃ©cieux corps sera transfÃ©rÃ© au paradis, pendant que ton Ã¢me sainte sera aux cieux dans les trÃ©sors de mon PÃ¨re, dans une clartÃ© supÃ©rieure, oÃ¹ sont la paix et la joie des anges saints et plus encore.Â»</span></i></span><span class=\"justification\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;(n. 39).</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn265\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref265\" name=\"_ftn265\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[265]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Giovanni BOSCO,<i>&nbsp;Memorie dellâ€™Oratorio&nbsp;</i>: pour lâ€™Ã©dition en langue franÃ§aise, cf. AndrÃ© BARUCQ,&nbsp;<i>Don Bosco, Souvenirs Autobiographiques</i>, Apostolat des Ã‰ditions, 1978, p. 98.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn266\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 16.133333206176758px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref266\" name=\"_ftn266\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.600000381469727px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[266]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.600000381469727px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Le grand sanctuaire de&nbsp;<i>La Consolata</i>&nbsp;se trouve Ã  Turin&nbsp;; mais de nombreux sanctuaires et chapelles lui sont aussi dÃ©diÃ©s tout autour de la capitale.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn267\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref267\" name=\"_ftn267\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[267]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;J</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">usquâ€™en 1862, il ne semble pas que Don Bosco fasse de faÃ§on habituelle mention du titre dâ€™<b>Auxiliatrice</b>&nbsp;ni de la victoire de LÃ©pante due prÃ©cisÃ©ment Ã  lâ€™Auxiliatrice. Cependant, en 1858, il avait dÃ©jÃ  employÃ© Â«&nbsp;<i>le titre&nbsp;<b>Auxilium Christianorum&nbsp;</b>pour souligner lâ€™action efficace de Marie, notre protectrice durant notre vie mais surtout au moment de notre mort&nbsp;Â».&nbsp;</i>Nous sommes quatre ans avant les&nbsp;<b>Â«&nbsp;faits de Spoleto&nbsp;Â»</b>&nbsp;(SpolÃ¨te) quand, en mars 1862,&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;dâ€™une ancienne effigie dans une Ã©glise en ruines (â€¦) la Vierge Marie avait parlÃ© Ã  un enfant de cinq ans et commenÃ§ait Ã  accorder des faveurs et des grÃ¢ces particuliÃ¨res.&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;Suite Ã  lâ€™enthousiasme suscitÃ© par ces faits, lâ€™archevÃªque de Spoleto</span>&nbsp;<i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Â«&nbsp;dÃ©crÃ©ta que fÃ»t donnÃ© Ã  cette image sainte le titre de Auxilium Christianorum&nbsp;Â»</span></i><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">. Ainsi se rÃ©pandit alors le culte de lâ€™Auxiliatrice. (Cf. Aldo GIRAUDO &amp; Giuseppe BIANCARDI,&nbsp;<i>Qui Ã¨ vissuto Don Bosco, Itinerari storico-geografici e spirituali</i>, Elle Di Ci, Torino-Leumann 2004, pp. 277-278.</span><span lang=\"IT\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn268\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref268\" name=\"_ftn268\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[268]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Mais il faut attendre Don Rua pour voir introduite dans la piÃ©tÃ© salÃ©sienne une Â«&nbsp;consÃ©cration Ã  Marie Auxiliatrice&nbsp;Â» en conclusion de la mÃ©ditation communautaire quotidienne, devenue aujourdâ€™hui, non plus&nbsp;<i>Â«&nbsp;consÃ©cration&nbsp;Â»</i>&nbsp;mais simplement Â«&nbsp;<i>priÃ¨re</i>&nbsp;Ã  Marie Auxiliatrice&nbsp;Â» (<i>preghiera di affidamento</i>).</span><span lang=\"IT\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn269\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref269\" name=\"_ftn269\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[269]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;MB XVIII, 258. CitÃ© dans lâ€™article 1 de nos Constitutions.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn270\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref270\" name=\"_ftn270\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[270]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Dominique Savio nâ€™Ã©tait arrivÃ© Ã  lâ€™Oratoire que depuis quelques semaines, le 29 octobre 1854.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn271\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref271\" name=\"_ftn271\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[271]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Cf.&nbsp;<i>Lumen Gentium</i>, chapitre VIII dÃ©jÃ  citÃ©.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn272\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref272\" name=\"_ftn272\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[272]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;Francis DESRAMAUT,&nbsp;<i>Cent mots de la spiritualitÃ© salÃ©sienne</i>, article&nbsp;<i>Marie</i>, p. 337.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div id=\"ftn273\"><p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\"><a href=\"applewebdata://EEA97CE2-51E1-4BD0-A058-618370CE509B#_ftnref273\" name=\"_ftn273\" title=\"\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span class=\"MsoFootnoteReference\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.1200008392334px;\">[273]</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"IT\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ibidem, p. 339.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div></div>		        \r\n            ', 2, '1569830713');
