ore: page;\"></span></b><div class=\"WordSection5\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">BLAGUE<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™ERREUR DE Lâ€™ERREUR<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><div><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" align=\"left\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0cm;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: 34.45pt; break-after: avoid; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 45.5pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">A<o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;un examen terminal des Ã©tudiants en mÃ©decine, le Professeur accueille le premier Ã©tudiant et lui adresse ceci&nbsp;: mon fils, quand un enfant de six mois pleure toute la nuit et a une tempÃ©rature Ã©levÃ©e accompagnÃ©e de la diarrhÃ©e, de quelle maladie sâ€™agit-il&nbsp;? La malaria rÃ©pondit-il. Il est fÃ©licitÃ©, et se montra prÃªt pour la question suivante. Comme tu connais dÃ©jÃ  la maladie, quel mÃ©dicament peux-tu lui prescrire&nbsp;?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™Ã©tudiant sans hÃ©siter&nbsp;&nbsp;rÃ©agit en disant camoquine liquide. Encore une fois il est louÃ©. Ayant ce cas dit le professeur, quelle dose proposerais-tu Ã  notre enfant&nbsp;? Ce dernier avec conviction dit une cuillÃ¨re de camoquine liquide. Le professeur dit câ€™est bon, pour toi lâ€™examen est fini tu peux appeler le suivant. Content des encouragements reÃ§us, il sorta et raconta Ã  ses camarades comment il a satisfait. Ã€ la derniÃ¨re question, ses amis lui disent que lâ€™enfant de cet Ã¢ge doit prendre la moitiÃ© et pas toute une cuillÃ¨re de camoquine liquide, va rectifier.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™Ã©tudiant se retrouve et rentre vite chez le professeur et lui dit, Ã  la derniÃ¨re question jâ€™ai commis une petite erreur&nbsp;; au lieu de dire la moitiÃ© dâ€™une cuillÃ¨re de liquide camoquine, jâ€™ai signifiÃ© la cuillÃ¨re entiÃ¨re. Le professeur sourit un peu et dit&nbsp;: mon fils, une petite erreur&nbsp;? Et pourtant lâ€™enfant devrait mourir&nbsp;! Câ€™est une grosse erreur parce que lâ€™enfant devrait mourir et tu en serais lâ€™auteur.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">En quoi tu lâ€™appelles petite, voilÃ  une seconde erreur<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><i>EugÃ¨ne BAHATI, sdb</i></b><i>.<o:p></o:p></i></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">POÃˆMES<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™enfant de la rue<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je nâ€™ai pas de pÃ¨re&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je nâ€™ai pas de mÃ¨re&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Un enfant sans culture,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Errant dans la nature.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ma famille mâ€™a abandonnÃ©,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Disant que je suis dÃ©sordonnÃ©.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ma vie est mise en doute,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi, fils de la route&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je passe la nuit Ã  la belle Ã©toile,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Le bistrot&nbsp;&nbsp;devient mon domicile&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Un enfant orphelin<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">ComparÃ© au fou de Berlin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je me dispute avec les insectes,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Les morceaux&nbsp; de viande et des miettes&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Un enfant sans souvenir,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Un enfant sans avenir.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je partage le repas avec les mouches&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Jâ€™ai une semaine sans prendre douche,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Un enfant sans trace,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Un enfant sans adresse.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Personne nâ€™est venu Ã  ma recherche&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Parce que je nâ€™ai quâ€™injures Ã  la bouche&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Aujourdâ€™hui Dieu me fait grÃ¢ce&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Vous voici devant ma face&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Quand vous vous divertissiez au loisir,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi, jâ€™Ã©tais en train de mourir,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je ne savais pas Ã  qui recourir&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ouf&nbsp;! Le ciel est venu Ã  mon secours&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">La nourriture que le cochon a laissÃ©e,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Mâ€™a servi de viatique la semaine passÃ©e.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Quand vous preniez du bon vin,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Jâ€™Ã©tais couchÃ© dans le ravin.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Quand vous fracassiez lâ€™omelette,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je broutais lâ€™herbe comme une bÃªte,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Jâ€™ai errÃ© dans la rue Ã§Ã  et lÃ &nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Dieu me rÃ©vÃ¨le lâ€™au-delÃ &nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">La nuit je menais une bataille.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Je faisais appel Ã  ma famille,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Autour de moi, des grenouilles,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Du haut de lâ€™arbre des abeilles&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi le moribond&nbsp;?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi le vagabond&nbsp;?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi le mÃ©prisÃ©&nbsp;?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi lâ€™apprivoisÃ©&nbsp;?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi le sauvage&nbsp;?&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Moi le moins sage&nbsp;?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ã” vie&nbsp;! Ã” mystÃ¨re&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">La rue nâ€™a jamais enfantÃ©&nbsp;!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Joannes Maria MASUMBUKO, sdb.<o:p></o:p></span></i></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™indigence du chef<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Le chef Lion avait son village prolÃ©taire<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Proche de la ville du maire LÃ©opard le beau.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Sa survie consistait en lâ€™exploitation des produits agraires<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Qui dâ€™auprÃ¨s de la ville lui valaient quelques pÃ©lauds.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Il en faisait usage moderne&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Un jour se paya un camion-citerne,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Facilitant le trafic de son huile de palme.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">La rÃ©ussite sourit au chef,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">GrÃ¢ce Ã  son exportation tout bÃ©nef,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™Ã©volution de ses travaux dâ€™huile de palme.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Gisant ainsi dans sa suffisance,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Le chef, de son village oublia indigence&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Entreprit le dessein Â«&nbsp;opÃ©ration propretÃ©&nbsp;Â»<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Proclamant le champ mÃ©tier vil&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Nommant son village peuplÃ© prochaine ville,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Il interdit tout travail au village causant viletÃ©.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">En fait, son opulence lâ€™avait rendu mÃ©chant<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Depuis que le peuple lui eut tournÃ© un dos mÃ©prisant.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ayant convenu de lui abandonner le village,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Tous les manieurs de houe et hache dÃ©sertÃ¨rent<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Et vers des contrÃ©es voisines migrÃ¨rent&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Et le chef sombra dans la solitude de son vÃ©tuste Ã¢ge.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Sa suffisance alimentaire peu Ã  peu devint paucitÃ©&nbsp;;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Plus personne pour manier machette, hache ou houe<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Et bientÃ´t, fringale dans sa bedaine tuant satiÃ©tÃ©,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Le richard trÃ©passa, tel un moucheron dans la boue.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Â«&nbsp;La vie est une scÃ¨ne et chacun en a son rÃ´le Ã  jouer&nbsp;!&nbsp;Â»<sup>&nbsp;<a href=\"applewebdata://38031EF4-AE25-4644-9BCC-525B63450FD7#_ftn7\" name=\"_ftnref7\" title=\"\"><sup><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">[7]</span></sup></a></sup><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Richard KAZADI, sdb.<o:p></o:p></i></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Les enfants qui meurent de faim</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Les enfants qui meurent de faim sont trÃ¨s bien Ã©levÃ©s.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ne parlent pas la bouche pleine.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ne gÃ¢chent jamais leur pain.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ne construisent pas des montagnes au bord de leurs assiettes.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ne font pas des caprices, car leur monde ne le leur permet pas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ne disent jamais&nbsp;: Â«&nbsp;je nâ€™aime pas Ã§a&nbsp;Â».<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ne font pas des grimaces quand on leur apporte un plat, par peur de le rater.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ne donnent mÃªme pas des os aux chiens, car ils en trouvent rarement.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils ont le cÅ“ur si lourd et le corps&nbsp;&nbsp;si fragile quâ€™ils vivent Ã  genoux, les yeux crevÃ©s, la bouche bÃ©ante.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Pour avoir le repas, ils attendent sagement car nous pouvons ou ne pas leur donner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils pleurent parfois quand Ã§a dure trop longtemps&nbsp;; pas parce quâ€™ils ont faim, mais parce quâ€™ils se souviennent de lâ€™attention familiale ratÃ©e.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Rassurez-vous, les enfants qui meurent de faim ne vont plus crier&nbsp;; ils en ont mal et nous ne les Ã©coutons pas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ces petits, sont bien Ã©levÃ©s vraiment.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils pleurent sans bruit, on ne les entend pas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils sont si petits quâ€™on ne les voit mÃªme pas.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils sont le quantum humain de nos jours.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils savent parfois de ne rien attendre de leurs pÃ¨res et de leurs mÃ¨res.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Riches de la terre, soyez tranquilles, ils ne vont plus crier.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils nâ€™en ont plus la force&nbsp;; mais malheureux vous Ãªtes si vous bouchez vos oreilles pour ne pas les Ã©couter.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils nâ€™ont plus dâ€™yeux, mÃªme pas de pieds, pas mÃªme de bras si non les vÃ´tres, les nÃ´tres.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Seuls leurs yeux, crevÃ©s de fatigue, de faim, de soif et des larmes peuvent parler&nbsp;; il suffit de les regarder.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils vont prendre la pause, ils vont mourir doucement sans bruit, sans danger.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Leurs images, leur souvenir gÃªneront et resteront gravÃ©s dans notre mÃ©moire&nbsp;; parce que, rongÃ©s des remords.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Ils en ont mal, mal et mal encore!!!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Les petits enfants qui meurent de faim sont trÃ¨s bien Ã©levÃ©s.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">DÃ©ogratias&nbsp;MURHULA, sdb.<o:p></o:p></span></i></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></i></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">KANSAS NEWS</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™annÃ©e pastorale et acadÃ©mique 2018-2019, annÃ©e de lâ€™ouverture du jubilÃ© du sexagÃ©naire de Kansebula a connu&nbsp;&nbsp;de changements considÃ©rables, le pÃ¨re David MUBENGA a Ã©tÃ© remplacÃ© par le pÃ¨re DieudonnÃ© BESA Ã  la direction gÃ©nÃ©rale de lâ€™institut supÃ©rieur de Philosophie saint Jean-Bosco, le pÃ¨re Patrick MPAMA a quant Ã  lui, remplacÃ© le pÃ¨re Antoine KABENGELE au secrÃ©tariat gÃ©nÃ©ral acadÃ©mique. Notons aussi que le PÃ¨re AimÃ© LULINDA a cÃ©dÃ© son fauteuil dâ€™Ã©conomat au frÃ¨re Patrice KANYEMA. Le pÃ¨re Daniel MAFUTA a Ã©tÃ© reconduit pour un second triennat&nbsp;&nbsp;Ã  la direction de la communautÃ©, le pÃ¨re Angelo POZZI a Ã©tÃ© nommÃ© animateur spirituel de la communautÃ©, le pÃ¨re Augustin MUYA assure une prÃ©sence fraternelle.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 35.4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Lâ€™ISPH a enrichi son corps profesoral en accueillant 13 nouveaux professeurs&nbsp;:&nbs